These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, bike, helicopter, tram
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, handball, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
2. the person driving the bike is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's sport is baseball is not the person driving the helicopter##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | bike   | tram    | bus    | helicopter |
| Sport      | volleyball | baseball | handball | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, mirinda, sprite
City: paris, london, miami, colone
1. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
3. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
4. the person drinking milk is not the person traveling to london##6
5. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | milk  | mirinda    | iced-tea | sprite    |
| Food       | colone | london | miami  | paris |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, amaryllis, zinnia, bellflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, electrician, police-officer
1. the person who growsbellflower is not the coach##6
2. the doctor is not the person who growszinnia##6
3. the electrician is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
4. the doctor is the person who growsdahlia##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the doctor##1
6. the person who growsdahlia is in an odd position##4
7. the coach is on the far left or far right##3
8. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | bellflower       | amaryllis  | dahlia  | zinnia |
| Job        | electrician | police-officer | doctor | coach  |

