.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, grapes, peas, watermelon
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway, train, trike
1. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
2. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the trike is not the person eating grapes##6
4. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | grapes | peas | watermelon     | spinach |
| Transport   | subway     | train    | quad-bike | trike    |

