.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
4 different games are played: chess, canasta, backgammon, whist
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, colombian, indian, polish
1. the australian is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing whist is not the colombian##6
3. the australian is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
5. the person playing backgammon is the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
7. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
8. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
9. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | canasta | backgammon    | chess  | whist   |
| Nationality   | indian  | polish | colombian | australian |

