4. the journalist is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
5. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the journalist##3
6. the coach is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
7. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
8. the person playing poker is not the social-worker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | poker  | canasta        | monopoly      | bridge          |
| Job        | coach | journalist | social-worker | photographer |

