2. the person driving the helicopter is not the pakistani##6
3. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the indian##5
4. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the subway is the indian##1
7. the polish is not the person driving the subway##6
8. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the pakistani##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | polish  | indian | pakistani    | indonesian |
| Transport   | helicopter | subway | skateboard | airplane  |

