.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, egyptian, japanese, indian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, surfing, swimming, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is golf is not the malaysian##6
2. the indian is on the left of the egyptian##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the indian is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the japanese is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6
6. the person who's sport is surfing is not the egyptian##6
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
8. the japanese is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | japanese | malaysian        | indian  | egyptian     |
| Sport   | golf     | weightlifting | surfing | swimming |

