.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, swisher, tiparillo, pall-mall
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, romance, time-travel, western
1. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the swisher-smoker##5
2. the swisher-smoker is not the person watching romance movies##6
3. the aristoff-smoker is the person watching western movies##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
5. the aristoff-smoker is between the swisher-smoker and the person watching adventure movies##2
6. the swisher-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | pall-mall | swisher      | aristoff | tiparillo   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | time-travel | western   | adventure |

