5. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who's sport is climbing##2
6. the person who's hobby is baking is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
