.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, juice
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, august, december, june
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person drinking fanta is not the person who's birthday is in august##6
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
8. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |       3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | juice    | iced-tea | hot-chocolate | fanta         |
| Sport      | august | december | february          | june |

