.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, horror, action, disaster
1. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
2. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
8. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | singing | skydiving | board-games | woodworking |
| Pet     | action  | horror      | western  | disaster       |

