.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, mirinda, water
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, coral, fuchsia, light-blue
1. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person who likes coral##5
6. the person who likes coral is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | iced-tea | water      | mirinda   |
| Transport   | light-blue  | coral   | fuchsia | blood-red |

 